From 1d567513bfd3b1a3baa6362b8532be99d0b0a300 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: forsen <gazikkamalov2@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Jul 2026 19:23:48 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] vtest: support exporting sync_file fds for venus sync
 points

New VCMD_SYNC_EXPORT_SYNC_FILE + VCMD_PARAM_HAS_VENUS_SYNC_FD. The vtest
server resolves a (sync_id, value) point to the pending timeline submit's
fence and exports a sync_file from its VkFence via the new
RENDER_CONTEXT_OP_EXPORT_FENCE render-server op (proxy translates fence_id
to seqno). Enables VK_KHR_external_fence_fd/semaphore_fd for venus-over-vtest
clients sharing the kernel with the server (LXC/container use case).
